FinBIF habitat types

Source: R/finbif_habitat_types.R
finbif_habitat_types.Rd

Display the habitat types and specific habitat types used in the FinBIF database.

finbif_habitat_types()

finbif_habitat_qualifiers()

Value

A data.frame.

Examples


# Display the administrative statuses used by FinBIF
finbif_habitat_types()
